# EventType: 15196011
#
# Descriptor: [Lambda_b0 -> (Lambda_c+ -> K- p+ pi+) ((D- -> K+ pi- pi-) || (D- -> K+ K- pi-))]cc
#
#
# NickName: Lb_LcD,LcKppi=DDalitz,DecProdCut,pCut1600MeV
#
# Cuts: DaughtersInLHCbAndWithMinP
#
# ExtraOptions: TracksInAccWithMinP
#
# Documentation: Lb->Lc+D- decay with Lc->Kpp+ and D->Kpipi or D->KKpi with DDalitz. Daughters in LHCb.
# EndDocumentation
#
# PhysicsWG: B2OC
# Tested: Yes
# Responsible: Philipp Ibis
# Email: philipp.ibis@cern.ch
# Date: 20170421
# CPUTime: < 1 min

# -------------------------
# DEFINE THE D+ AND D-
# -------------------------
Alias      MyD+  D+
Alias      MyD-  D-
ChargeConj MyD+  MyD-

# -------------------------
# THEN DEFINE THE Lc+ AND Lc~-
# -------------------------
Alias      MyLambda_c+       Lambda_c+
Alias      Myanti-Lambda_c-  anti-Lambda_c-
ChargeConj MyLambda_c+       Myanti-Lambda_c-

# ---------------
# DECAY OF THE Lb
# ---------------
Decay Lambda_b0sig
  1.000       MyLambda_c+ MyD-     PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay anti-Lambda_b0sig

# ---------------
# DECAY OF THE D+
# ---------------
Decay MyD+
  0.700  K-  pi+  pi+                 D_DALITZ;
  0.300  K-  K+  pi+                 D_DALITZ;
Enddecay
CDecay MyD-
#

# ---------------
# DECAY OF THE Lc
# ---------------

Decay MyLambda_c+
  1.000  K-  p+  pi+   PHSP;
Enddecay
CDecay Myanti-Lambda_c-
#
End
